/**************************************************/
    How to test a word count Program ?
/**************************************************/

    We can use following test cases:
        
        1. No Input 
            then Ouput will be like: Newlines words characters
                                     0        0     0
        2. One charater word
                                     1        1     2( 1 character + a newline character )
        3. two character word        
                                     1        1     3( 2 characters + newline character )
        4. 2 One-character words
                                     1        2     4
        5. No words just newlines

        6. No words just tabs, blanks, and new lines.
        
        7. one word per line
        
        8. word starting after some blanks

******************************************************
